channel.title: [508]NeedGp skilling and pvp[508]
channel.description:
Well, I was on a bulby server the other day and someone told me that bulby was so unstable, I decided to say bye bulby and start a NEW source, other than palidino and bulby or espeon, I wanna make a new source called NeedGp :D Because NeedGp stands for poor people begging for money, and I want this to be a very organized server so that everyone can learn from it. So basically I'm making a noob friendly server. :P Some of these pics are gonna be on new server so i'm not gonna remove em.
green = Completed.
[font=courier]------PVP----- Working Dragon Claws [color=green]Working Rune C'bow[/color] [color=green]Working Dragonfire Shield[/color] [color=green]Working Dark Bow[/color] [color=green]Working Godswords[/color] Working Vengeance Working Barrows [color=green]Working Pots[/color] [color=green]Working Food[/color] [color=green]Added Bounty Hunter[/color][/font]
[size=10pt]/****PvN****\ New Aggressive Npc's New Slayer Base New Combat base towards Npc's New working Prayer against npc's[/size] /******Skilling*****\ New Almost Full Crafting (just have to add jewel crafting) New Smithing Base (use bar on anvil blah blah blah) New Fletching Base with correct interfaces (make bows) Basic Runecrafting (tele to abyss and make your runes) New Woodcutting with great timers :D New Mining with great timers :D (adding it later tonight)
[size=12pt]/******Other Upgrades******\ New Clan Chat with ranks Full Bank Setup New Trading Base New Economy More Trainable Areas (because old bulby/david servers had few places to train on :D) More Variety of drops from Npc's (for economic purposees)[/size]/*****Connection stuffs*****\ New connectionmanager/anti-flood Only allow 2 connections per IP address, You can easily fix this, I use it for pvp testing.
